cast.overview: When the popular, restless Landon Carter is forced to participate in the school drama production, he falls in love with Jamie Sullivan, the daughter of the town's minister. Jamie has a "to-do" list for her life, as well as a very big secret she must keep from Landon.
cast.title: A Walk to Remember

details.biography:
Sheila Brothers is an American producer, animator, actress, and sometimes stunt performer.

She was the morning show host for The Sunny Morning Show in Wilmington, NC on WILT-FM and editor of the Wilmington film online magazine, "The Wilmywood Daily" until the end of 2018.

She has worn many hats in the film industry including directing, writing, producing, acting and her favorite: stunt work.
details.name: Sheila Brothers
